        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 8. Proserpinicaris wangpi sp. nov., scanning electron micrographs, (A) holotype male; (B) paratype male; (C and D) allotype female. (A) Fifth pedigerous and genital somites, ventral view; (B) fifth legs, lateral view; (C) habitus, lateral view; (D) anal somite and caudal rami, lateral view. Scale bars 20 µm for (C), 10 µm for (A, D), 3 µm for (B)." ;
